# BrewFlow — Design System

Premium coffee shop experience inspired by modern urban spaces.

The design focuses on:
- minimalism
- elegance
- calm visual hierarchy
- high-end café aesthetic

---

## 1. Design Principles

### 1.1 Minimal but expressive
Avoid clutter. Every element should have a purpose.

### 1.2 Premium feel
Use whitespace, typography, and muted tones instead of heavy UI.

### 1.3 Calm interaction
No aggressive colors, no sharp contrasts, no noise.

### 1.4 Fast comprehension
Users should understand:
- what to order
- how to order
- what’s happening with their order

in seconds.

