## 3. Typography

### Font Families

- **Primary (UI):** Inter
- **Display (Headings):** Playfair Display

---

### Scale

| Element         | Style                          |
|-----------------|-------------------------------|
| Hero title      | 3rem – 5rem (Playfair)        |
| Section title   | 1.8rem – 2.4rem               |
| Card title      | 1.1rem – 1.3rem               |
| Body text       | 1rem                          |
| Secondary text  | 0.85rem – 0.95rem             |

---

### Rules

- Use **Playfair Display only for impact**
- Keep body text clean and readable
- Avoid heavy bold usage

---

## 4. Spacing System

Use consistent spacing:

| Size | Value |
|------|------|
| xs   | 4px  |
| sm   | 8px  |
| md   | 12px |
| lg   | 16px |
| xl   | 24px |
| xxl  | 32px |

---

### Layout rules

- Sections: `24px – 56px` vertical spacing
- Cards padding: `16px – 24px`
- Grid gaps: `20px – 24px`

---

## 5. Components

### 5.1 Cards (`.bf-card`)

Used across:
- products
- admin orders
- featured sections

Style:
- soft background (`--surface`)
- subtle shadow
- rounded corners
- generous padding

---

### 5.2 Buttons

#### Primary
- filled
- rounded (pill shape)
- background: `--primary`
- text: white

#### Secondary
- outlined
- neutral tone
- used for secondary actions

---

### 5.3 Chips / Filters

Used in:
- categories
- admin filters

States:
- default → neutral
- active → primary background + white text

---

### 5.4 Status Chips

| Status     | Style |
|------------|------|
| RECEIVED   | neutral |
| PREPARING  | warning |
| READY      | success |
| COMPLETED  | muted |

---

### 5.5 Modal

Used for:
- product details

Rules:
- centered
- image-first layout
- large typography
- minimal clutter

---

### 5.6 Drawer (Cart)

- slides from right
- persistent state
- clear CTA (checkout)

---

